controls.control_description:
While offering foreign exchange market-making facilities to users, SPDs shall
comply with the provisions of the Foreign Exchange Management Act 1999, and all
rules, regulations and directions issued thereunder;

Aggregate exposure to a counterparty comprising
both on and off-balance sheet exposures shall be calculated based on the method
prescribed for capital computation in these Directions;

On receipt of the credit
event payment, (a) the underlying asset shall be removed from the books if it has
been delivered to the protection seller;
